, 
<figureCitation box="[1143,1193,1015,1041]" captionStart="FIGURE 97" captionStartId="199.[151,250,1355,1379]" captionTargetBox="[151,1437,181,1332]" captionTargetId="figure-15@199.[151,1437,181,1332]" captionTargetPageId="199" captionText="FIGURE 97. Environment of and collecting sites at Nyingchi area. A. Sign of Yigong Tea Farm (ƌŭē厂). B. Forest near Yigong. C. Forest at Pailong Township (ḦË乡). D. Forest near Tongmai Town (ȃ9W)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6340967" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6340967/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">97C</figureCitation>
).
